    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It is functional and drivable but shows noticeable wear on both the interior and exterior. There are some mechanical issues that may require attention, and buyers should be prepared for potential repair costs. Overall, it is a usable vehicle but not without its flaws.",
      "price": 20000.0,
